refer here https://stackoverflow.com/questions/48387180/is-it-possible-to-capitalize-first-letter-of-text-string-in-react-native-how-to

Write a function like this

          Capitalize(str){
          return str.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + str.slice(1);
          }

then call it from <Text> tag By passing text as parameter

          <Text>{this.Capitalize(this.state.title)} </Text>
